Fix missing buttons in Find In Page bar
pull_request.body:
1. Move the corresponding icon assets to the DesginSystem module so that
    they can be found at runtime.

2. When the user hasn't entered any text, the previous/next buttons were
    not made disabled, which could be a little bit misleading and was not
    consistent with the case where there are no search results.

Fixes #3699

commits.message:
Move nimbus-fml.sh script to Application Services (#3890)

* Remove nimbus-fml.sh in favour of application-services version

* Removed now redundant .experimenter.yaml

* move to source_root

pull_request.title: Move nimbus-fml.sh script to Application Services
pull_request.body:
Fixes [EXP-3953](https://mozilla-hub.atlassian.net/browse/EXP-3953).

This removes:

- the `nimbus-fml.sh` in favour of a copy downloaded by `checkout.sh` from the Application Services repo.
- the `.experimenter.yaml` file which is no longer needed by experimenter. Experimenter now deals with the FML file directly.

It also ensures that the FML file is processed on every build, instead of when the `nimbus.fml.yaml` file is changed.

issue.title: Add url invalid character api for iOS 17
issue.body: iOS 17 changes what is classified as a valid URL. This could cause breaking changes in the app so this PR replaces all URL inits with an API that disables the new behavior.

comment.body: All tests pass on both iPhone and iPad on XCode 15.0.1 and iOS 17.0.1 simulator. 😄
